docs.lead_paragraph: Candidates hungry for votes in one pivotal Ohio county often spice up their quest with Cincinnati-style chili. If they're in the northwest part of the state, hot dogs made famous on the TV show "M.A.S.H." are on the menu. If in Cleveland, they're likely to find themselves poring over the eclectic choices at the West Side Market.
